            <div class="shell text-left">
                <h4 class="text-bold">Privacy Policy & Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA)</h4>
                <hr class="divider bg-madison hr-sm-left-0">
                <div class="offset-top-30">
                    <h5 class="text-bold">Data Collection & Usage</h5>
                    <p class="offset-top-15">We collect and process personal data including:</p>
                    <ul class="list-marked list-marked-primary">
                        <li><strong>Identity Data:</strong> Name, IC/passport, date of birth, nationality</li>
                        <li><strong>Contact Data:</strong> Address, phone, email</li>
                        <li><strong>Education Data:</strong> Academic records, qualifications, transcripts</li>
                        <li><strong>Financial Data:</strong> Payment information, billing details</li>
                        <li><strong>Electronic Data:</strong> IP address, cookies, device information</li>
                        <li><strong>Behavioral Data:</strong> Website usage, preferences</li>
                        <li><strong>Marketing Preferences:</strong> Communication consent</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-40">
                    <h5 class="text-bold">Legal Basis for Processing</h5>
                    <ul class="list-marked list-marked-primary">
                        <li><strong>Contract Performance:</strong> Enrollment and education delivery</li>
                        <li><strong>Legal Obligations:</strong> Compliance with regulations (SEAB, ICA, SSG)</li>
                        <li><strong>Legitimate Interests:</strong> Administrative and operational purposes</li>
                        <li><strong>Consent:</strong> Marketing and optional communications</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-40">
                    <h5 class="text-bold">Your Rights</h5>
                    <ul class="list-marked list-marked-primary">
                        <li><strong>Access:</strong> Request copy of your personal data</li>
                        <li><strong>Correction:</strong> Update inaccurate information</li>
                        <li><strong>Deletion:</strong> Request erasure (subject to legal requirements)</li>
                        <li><strong>Withdraw Consent:</strong> Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
                        <li><strong>Data Portability:</strong> Receive data in machine-readable format</li>
                        <li><strong>Object:</strong> Object to automated decision-making</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-40">
                    <h5 class="text-bold">Cookies & Analytics</h5>
                    <p>We use cookies, Google Analytics, and third-party pixels for website functionality, analytics, and marketing. You can manage cookie preferences in your browser.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-40">
                    <h5 class="text-bold">Third-Party Sharing & Cross-Border Transfer</h5>
                    <p>Personal data may be shared with:</p>
                    <ul class="list-marked list-marked-primary">
                        <li>Examination boards (SEAB, CIE, Edexcel)</li>
                        <li>Government agencies (ICA, MOE)</li>
                        <li>Service providers (IT, payment processing, insurance)</li>
                        <li>Universities (for applications with your consent)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-40">
                    <h5 class="text-bold">Children's Data</h5>
                    <p>For students under 18, we require parental/guardian consent for data collection and processing.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-40">
                    <h5 class="text-bold">Data Security & Breach Notification</h5>
                    <p>We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your data. In case of a data breach, affected individuals and relevant authorities will be notified promptly.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-40">
                    <h5 class="text-bold">Data Retention</h5>
                    <p>Personal data is retained as required by law and regulatory bodies, typically for 7 years after course completion or as mandated by SSG/MOE.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-40" style="background: #e3f2fd; padding: 20px; border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;">
                    <h6 class="text-bold">Contact Our Data Protection Officer (DPO)</h6>
                    <p>For privacy inquiries or to exercise your rights: <strong>dpo@esic.edu.sg</strong></p>
                </div>
                <div class="offset-top-50 text-center">
                    <a class="btn btn-default" href="admissions.html">Back to Admissions</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
